      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior upholstery, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically robust and aesthetically unrivaled, it offers an acquisition opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a definitive standard of excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
